<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><hymn_number>176</hymn_number>
<lyrics>[V1]
 Pathian thaw, nang ka chem, Nunnak thar ka pe tuah, Na duhmi le na
 tuanmi kha, Ka tuan khawh ve nak-hnga.

[V2]
 Pathian thaw, nang ka chem, Ka lung a thian hlan tiang, Nang he
 lungthin khat ka put tiang, Tuan awk le innak ah.

[V3]
 Pathian thaw, nang ka chem, Na mi ka si tiangin, Vawlei sermi ka pumsa
 hi, Na mei in lumter tuah.

[V4]
 Pathian thaw, nang ka chem, Ka thi bal ti lai lo; Sihmanhsehlaw
 zungzal nunnak, Na sinah ka hmuh lai.</lyrics>
<key>F</key>
<title>PATHIAN THAW, NANG KA CHEM CH176</title>
</song>